{
  "text": "It is characteristic of our study that FDs thought that continuous training was still necessary although most of them had passed advanced training in depression. For comparison, according to a study of Soykan, only those physicians interested in psychiatry had passed training in depression [CITATION_1] . It shows that our FDs recognise the need for dealing with the problem and are often engaged in it in their daily work.",
